snippet.title: 'Special Mission (特种任务)' Flash game playthrough
snippet.description:
Because I couldn't find a video of anyone actually completing this!
This is a rough playthrough of all three difficulties, Easy, Normal (4:01) and Hard (8:36). I played Hard at half-speed (hence the dubbed-over audio) but still couldn't beat the boss. Welp!
